<li>Germany: <a href="https://alexa.amazon.de">https://alexa.amazon.de</a></li>
<li>Japan: <a href="https://alexa.amazon.co.jp">https://alexa.amazon.co.jp</a></li>
<li>Canada: <a href="https://alexa.amazon.ca">https://alexa.amazon.ca</a></li>
<li>Australia: <a href="https://alexa.amazon.com.au">https://alexa.amazon.com.au</a></li>
<li>India: <a href="https://alexa.amazon.in">https://alexa.amazon.in</a></li>
<li>Spain: <a href="https://alexa.amazon.es">https://alexa.amazon.es</a></li>
</ul>
